      "raw_text": "Owing to the Illness of Attorney\nCannon, of the Northern Pacific,\nthe scheduled meeting of the bridge\ncommittee of the city council call\ned for consideration of grade sepa-\nration plans. did not materialize.\n1t is unauthorativel stated that\nthe railroad will agree to open\nBrowne st. and also to make some\nother changes which city officials\ndesire. The meeting will be held\nsoon after New Year."
